ds|Golden Orange]] ([[International Antalya Golden Orange Film Festival]], Turkey) *[[Golden Raspberry Awards]] *[[Governors Awards]] ([[Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]]) *[[Goya Awards]] (Spain) *[[Guldbagge Awards]] (Sweden) *[[Hollywood Walk of Fame]] *[[Humanitas Prize]] *[[Independent Spirit Awards]] *[[Indonesian Film Festival]] *[[International Indian Film Academy Awards]] (India) *[[Deutsche Filmakademie|Lola Awards]] ([[Deutsche Filmakademie|German Film Academy]]) *[[Lux Style Awards]] (Pakistan) *[[Luna Awards]] ([[Film Academy of the Philippines]]) * [[MTV Movie & TV Awards]] * [[National Film Awards UK]] *[[National Film Awards]] (India) *[[New York Film Festival]] *[[Palme d'Or]] ([[Cannes Film Festival]], France) *[[San Diego Film Awards]] ([[Film Consortium San Diego]]) *[[Screen Actors Guild Award]]s ([[Screen Actors Guild]]) *[[Screen Awards]] (India) *[[Shooting Stars Award]] ([[Berlin International Film Festival]]) *[[XBIZ Award]] – [[Pornography|adult industry]] *[[XRCO Award]]s &ndash; to people working in adult entertainment ([[X-Rated Critics Organization]]) *[[Young Artist Award]]s (Young Artist Association) }}
