al Television Society awards]] ([[Royal Television Society]]) *[[Soap Opera Digest Awards|''Soap Opera Digest'' Awards]] *[[Soapy Awards]] *[[Academy of Television Arts & Sciences#Television Academy Honors|Television Academy Honors]] ([[Academy of Television Arts & Sciences]]) *[[Young Artist Award]]s ([[Young Artist Association]]) {{div col end}}
