'''James Madison''' (born 1956/57) was the '''Mad Hatter''' who robbed 17 banks while wearing a variety of hats. He was apprehended on July 17, 2007, in [[Newark, New Jersey]], USA, shortly after police tracked his car license plates.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amw.com/fugitives/brief.cfm?id=43932|title=amw.com - James Madison - Fugitive<!-- Bot generated title -->|publisher=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070724180820/http://www.amw.com/fugitives/brief.cfm?id=43932|archivedate=2007-07-24|df=}}</ref> His ''modus operandi'' was to wear a different hat for each robbery.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,290381,00.html|title='mad Hatter' Bank Robber Arrested, Identified|date=23 July 2007|publisher=}}</ref>

