'''Salal Bugti''' was born in [[Quetta]], [[Balochistan (Pakistan)|Balochistan]] on December 23, 1969.{{Fact|date=June 2008}}

He was assassinated in June 1992 on Jinnah Road, [[Quetta]] by members of the [[Kalpar]] tribe{{Citation needed|date=August 2012}}, a sub-clan of the [[Bugti]] tribe opposed to [[Nawab Akbar Bugti]]. He was Nawab Bugti's second last child and last son from his first wife (who is of [[Bugti]] origin).{{Fact|date=June 2008}}

